n font-icon-doubled-halved-extra-small"></i>Easily doubled / halved</li><li class="vegetarian last"><i class="font-icon font-icon-vegetarian-extra-small"></i>Vegetarian</li></ul></div><div class="recipe-header__nutrition"><h3 class="recipe-header__nutrition-title"><strong>Nutrition:</strong> per serving (6)</h3><ul class="nutrition" itemprop="nutrition" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/NutritionInformation"><li><span class="nutrition__label">kcal</span><span class="nutrition__value" itemprop="calories">262</span></li><li><span class="nutrition__label">fat</span><span class="nutrition__value" itemprop="fatContent">14g</span></li><li><span class="nutrition__label">saturates</span><span class="nutrition__value" itemprop="saturatedFatContent">9g</span></li><li><span class="nutrition__label">carbs</span><span class="nutrition__value" itemprop="carbohydrateContent">29g</span></li><li><span class="nutrition__label">sugars</span><span class="nutrition__value" itemprop="sugarContent">0.3g</span></li><li><span class="nutrition__label">fibre</span><span class="nutrition__value" itemprop="fiberContent">1g</span></li><li><span class="nutrition__label">protein</span><span class="nutrition__value" itemprop="proteinContent">4g</span></li><li><span class="nutrition__label nutrition__label--low">salt</span><span class="nutrition__value" itemprop="sodiumContent">0.4g</span></li></ul></div></div></div> </section><div class="recipe-header__actions"><div class="flyout"><a href="/user/login" class="btn btn--primary btn--save btn--block btn--icon-right" rel="nofollow"><span class="btn__text">Save <span class="wide-only">to My Good Food</span></span></a><div class="flyout__content"><div class="flyout__content-inner">Please <a href="/user/login?destination=node/100617">sign in</a> or <a href="/user/register?destination=node/100617">register</a> to save recipes.</div></div></div><div class="recipe-header__print"> <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn btn--default btn--icon-right btn--print"> <span class="btn__text">Print</span> <i class="font-icon font-icon-print"></i> </a></div></div></div> </header><div class="grid-padding"><div class="col span8"><div id="ad-mpu-premium-1-narrow" class="ad-mpu-premium-1-narrow"><div class="ad ad--mpu-premium-1-narrow" id="ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_narrow-e01a1a0bf8"><script type="text/javascript">Drupal.GPT.createSlot("ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_narrow-e01a1a0bf8", function () {var m = Drupal.GPT.buildSizeMapping([[[0,0],[[300,250]]],[[480,0],[[300,250],[300,600]]],[[770,0],[]]]);var s = googletag.defineSlot(Drupal.GPT.unitPath(), m.define, "ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_narrow-e01a1a0bf8").defineSizeMapping(m.mapping.build()).setTargeting("pos", ["mpu_premium_1"]).addService(googletag.pubads());});</script></div></div><div id="recipetools" class="constantco-widget section-recipetools" data-app-resource-id="100617" data-type="recipetools" data-params="mobile_breakpoint=821"></div><div id="responsive-tabs" class="responsive-tabs responsive-tabs--2"><ul class="responsive-tabs__tabs"><li class="responsive-tabs__tab is-active"> <a href="#recipe-ingredients">Ingredients</a></li><li class="responsive-tabs__tab"> <a href="#recipe-method">Method</a></li></ul><div class="responsive-tabs__panes"> <section id="recipe-ingredients" class="responsive-tabs__pane is-active"><h2 class="responsive-tabs__pane-title">Ingredients</h2><div class="ingredients-list"><div class="ingredients-list__content"><ul class="ingredients-list__group"><li class="ingredients-list__item" itemprop="ingredients" content="225g plain flour">225g plain flour</li><li class="ingredients-list__item" itemprop="ingredients" content="100g butter, diced">100g <a href="/glossary/butter" class="ingredients-list__glossary-link" data-tooltip-content="#ingredients-glossary &gt; article" data-tooltip-width="350" data-tooltip-hide-delay="200" data-tooltip-flyout="true">butter</a>, diced<span class="ingredients-list__glossary-element" id="ingredients-glossary"><article id="node-261201" role="main" class="node node-glossary-item node-teaser node-teaser clearfix main row grid-padding"><div class="node-image"> <a href="/glossary/butter"><img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/bbcgf_thumbnail_search/public/glossary/butter.jpg?itok=WmVkxpe0" width="100" height="100" alt="Butter" title="Butter" /></a></div><h2 class="node-title node-glossary-title"><a href="/glossary/butter">Butter</a></h2> <span class="fonetic text-style-alt">butt-err</span><p>Butter is made when lactic-acid producing bacteria are added to cream and churned to make an…</p> </article></span></li><li class="ingredients-list__item" itemprop="ingredients" content="pinch salt">pinch salt</li></ul></div></div> </section> <section id="recipe-method" class="responsive-tabs__pane"><h2 class="responsive-tabs__pane-title">Method</h2><div class="method"><div class="method__actions"> <button role="button" class="btn btn--default btn--icon-right inline-video" data-video-id="3802739667001" data-player-id="777b296f-1c59-4fff-a252-cd121cdebe7d" data-account-id="1786863135"><span class="btn__text">Watch recipe video</span><i class="font-icon font-icon-play"></i></button></div><ol class="method__list"><li class="method__item" itemprop="recipeInstructions"><p><a href="https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/content/test-best-flour-shakers">Sift</a> the flour into a large <a href="https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/content/test-best-rolling-pins">bowl</a>, add the butter and rub in with your fingertips until the mixture resembles fine breadcrumbs.</p></li><li class="method__item" itemprop="recipeInstructions"><p>Stir in the salt, then add 2-3 tbsp water and <a href="https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/content/top-five-food-mixers">mix</a> to a firm dough. Knead the dough briefly and gently on a floured surface. Wrap in cling film and chill while preparing the filling.</p></li></ol></div> <footer class="recipe-info"><div class="recipe-info__publication">Recipe from Good Food Vegetarian Christmas, <a href="/search/recipes/date/1164931200" class="text-style-alt">December 2006</a></div> <a class="recipe-info__magazine-ad" href=" https://www.buysubscriptions.com/print/bbc-good-food-magazine-subscription?promo=GFBS718&style=Brand&utm_medium=brandsite&utm_source=bbcgoodfood.com&utm_campaign=recipe_GFBS718_Brand&utm_content=recipe-banner" rel="external" onclick="Drupal.GFAnalytics.trackEvent(['Magazines', 'subscribe', 'Recipe' ])"> <img src="https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/magazine/gf_aug18_337x109.jpg" alt="BBC GoodFood Magazine" /> </a> </footer> </section></div></div><div class="recipe__tips"><div class="field field-name-field-bbcgf-tips field-type-entityreference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><div class="view view-recipe-views view-id-recipe_views view-display-id-tips view-dom-id-b9b26c0634d7eba5b343f0b0c44d7e34"><div class="view-content"><div class="carousel-tips__wrapper carousel"><div class="flexslider carousel-tips__elements" data-type="carousel-tips"><ul class="slides carousel-tips__slides"><li class="carousel-tips__single-slide "><div class="carousel-tips__single-slide-content"><h3>Recipe Tip</h3><h4><span class="field-content">Proportions</span></h4><div class="carousel-tips__single-slide-body show-more__content">To make more or less, remember the proportions - half fat to flour - and don&#39;t add too much water or the pastry will be hard. If other dry ingredients are included in the recipe, add them at the same time as the salt.</div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> <section id="block-bbcgf-search-views-bbcgf-cc-rel-recipes" class="section-box section-box--you-may-also-like"> <header class="section-box__header"><h2 class="section-box__title">You may also like</h2> </header><div class="section-box__content"><div class="carousel"><div class="flexslider type-1" data-type="1"><ul class="slides"><li class=""><article id="node-100409" class="node node-recipe node-ca